  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">• Characteristics of LHD neutron diagnostics were evaluated by MCNP-6 and FENDL-3.0. • The detection efficiencies are almost insensitive to the neutron source profile. • The detection efficiencies for 252 Cf neutrons and for the plasma neutrons were evaluated. • The response function of the stilbene detector was evaluated with PHITS code. • The special resolution of the vertical neutron camera was estimated to be 70 mm.</subfield>
